Linux Setup

Install Linux OS on your local system ‚Äî as Linux is as secure as your blood!

Ways to set up Linux:

1. Virtual Box or Oracle VM ‚Äì Make a virtual box of Oracle and install image of Linux (.iso file).
2. Vagrant Tool ‚Äì Vagrant can help using Linux virtually.
3. WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux) ‚Äì Windows now gives Linux support also within Windows (included in Windows 10 and 11).
4. Dual Boot ‚Äì We can install Linux alongside Windows and choose at startup which OS to use.
5. Cloud Setup ‚Äì We can make our Linux run on cloud services like AWS, Azure, or GCP.

‚úÖ We will be going ahead with option (5)

